body_html:
Hey!
Something similar happens to me recently with a really simple convolutional encoder. The ".tflite" file exported with this:
https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1KMQQjuSfurog3n-Ut7BMSfv1TXGFonbX#scrollTo=WZlb35eHCchl

And executed with "implementation 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-lite:+'" in Android was almost twice slow than the exported as a usual ".pb" and executed with "implementation 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-android:+'" in Android.
